title: EulerLettreDigital to be released
text: A new Opera Bernoulli Euler digital platform will be launched at Saturday 24. Feb 2024 noon. It will start with to publish all volumes of Euler Opera Omnia and search functionality. The platform will be continually enhanced by the latest AI from Lettre AI and will be open for further development and contributions. Interested in the project? You can sign in for the newsletter and get the latest news and updates.
